{"word":"Sharon","slug":"sharon","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Sharon</b> <a href=\"#/H8289\">H8289</a> <br/> 1. The maritime slope of Palestine north of Joppa:<br/> - David's herds in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=27&verse=29'>1Ch 27:29</a> <br/> - Roses and beauty of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=22&chapter=2&verse=1'>Son 2:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=33&verse=9'>Isa 33:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=35&verse=2'>Isa 35:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=65&verse=10'>Isa 65:10</a> <br/> - Called Saron<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=9&verse=35'>Act 9:35</a> <br/> 2. A place of unascertained location<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=5&verse=16'>1Ch 5:16</a>"}]}